These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-1::.
There 7 different types of food: apple, apricot, kiwi, pineapple, radish, raspberry, spinach
The people have 7 different jobs:  journalist, chef, electrician, dressmaker, lawyer, librarian, pilot
 1. the person eating kiwi is on the far left##1
 2. the person eating pineapple is not the librarian##6
 3. the journalist is on the left of the person eating apricot##1
 4. the pilot is somewhere to the right of the lawyer##5
 5. the person eating radish is on the left or right of the person eating spinach##3
 6. the journalist is on the right of the person eating kiwi##1
 7. the person eating raspberry is somewhere between the person eating apricot and the chef##7
 8. the chef is on the left of the pilot##1
 9. the dressmaker is somewhere between the person eating radish and the electrician##7
10. the electrician is on the left or right of the journalist##3
11. the lawyer is on the far left##1
12. the person eating pineapple is somewhere to the left of the pilot##5
13. the person eating pineapple is somewhere to the right of the person eating raspberry##5
14. the person eating spinach is somewhere to the right of the person eating radish##5
15. the person eating radish is the chef##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4     |     5     |     6     |    7    |
| Food          | kiwi    | apple    | apricot | raspberry | pineapple | radish    | spinach |
| Job   | lawyer | journalist | electrician  | librarian   | dressmaker    | chef | pilot |

