.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-2::.
There 7 different types of food: artichoke, banana, cabbage, grapefruit, pomegranate, radish, zucchini
The people have 7 different jobs:  musician, scientist, nurse, journalist, bartender, firefighter, security-guard
 1. the firefighter is somewhere between the person eating zucchini and the person eating banana##7
 2. the security-guard is the person eating grapefruit##1
 3. the bartender is on the right of the security-guard##1
 4. the security-guard is on the right of the person eating radish##1
 5. the person eating artichoke is somewhere between the journalist and the scientist##7
 6. the person eating radish is somewhere between the person eating grapefruit and the nurse##7
 7. the person eating pomegranate is somewhere between the person eating grapefruit and the person eating banana##7
 8. the musician is on the right of the journalist##1
 9. the bartender is somewhere to the left of the person eating pomegranate##5
10. the person eating pomegranate is somewhere to the right of the firefighter##5
11. the firefighter is not the person eating zucchini##6
12. the scientist is on the right of the firefighter##1
13. the bartender is between the journalist and the person eating grapefruit##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |       5       |      6      |    7    |
| Food    | zucchini  | cabbage | radish | grapefruit | artichoke     | pomegranate | banana  |
| Job   | nurse | firefighter | scientist  | security-guard  | bartender | journalist      | musician |

