.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-3::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, milk, cola, almond-milk, lemonade, sprite, mirinda
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: ambient, blues, country, d&b, hip-hop, jazz, metal
 1. the fan of metal is between the person drinking cola and the fan of country##2
 2. the person drinking milk is somewhere to the right of the fan of blues##5
 3. the fan of blues is not the person drinking almond-milk##6
 4. the fan of ambient is somewhere to the right of the fan of jazz##5
 5. the fan of ambient is between the fan of jazz and the person drinking lemonade##2
 6. the fan of country is somewhere to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##5
 7. the person drinking mirinda is on the far right##1
 8. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the fan of d&b##3
 9. the person drinking cola is somewhere between the fan of hip-hop and the fan of metal##7
10. the fan of blues is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
11. the person drinking lemonade is in an even position##4
12. the person drinking lemonade is not the fan of ambient##6
13. the person drinking sprite is somewhere between the person drinking milk and the person drinking lemonade##7
14. the fan of d&b is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
15. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
16. the person drinking lemonade is not the fan of jazz##6
17. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the fan of country##3
18. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
19. the fan of ambient is somewhere to the left of the fan of hip-hop##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |     3     |    4    |       5       |     6     |      7      |
| Beverage         | hot-chocolate | milk | sprite | lemonade  | cola | almond-milk | mirinda |
| Music-Genre   | blues   | jazz       | ambient   | hip-hop | d&b           | metal     | country     |

