 4. the person who likes pink is somewhere to the right of the person driving the trike##5
 5. the person who likes grey is somewhere to the left of the person who likes amber##5
 6. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 7. the person driving the scooter is somewhere between the person driving the quad-bike and the person driving the snowmobile##7
 8. the person who likes grey is on the far left##1
 9. the person driving the snowmobile is somewhere to the left of the person who likes ebony##5
10. the person who likes coral is in an even position##4
11. the person who likes coral is somewhere between the person who likes pink and the person who likes azure##7
12. the person driving the skateboard is somewhere to the right of the person who likes amber##5
13. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
14. the person who likes emerald is somewhere to the left of the person driving the van##5
15. the person who likes amber is on the left or right of the person driving the skateboard##3
16. the person driving the snowmobile is somewhere to the left of the person driving the scooter##5
17. the person driving the skateboard is between the person who likes coral and the person driving the trike##2
18. the person who likes pink is not the person driving the van##6
