 3. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in july is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in march and the person who's birthday is in may##7
 5. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in april is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 7. the person who's sport is surfing is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in february##5
 8. the person who's sport is basketball is not the person who's birthday is in april##6
 9. the person who's birthday is in february is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##5
10. the person who's sport is snowboarding is not the person who's birthday is in april##6
11. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left or right of the person who's sport is biathlon##3
12. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left or right of the person who's sport is soccer##3
13. the person who's birthday is in may is not the person who's sport is biathlon##6
14. the person who's birthday is in february is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
15. the person who's sport is biathlon is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in february##5
16. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
