 3. the person playing domino is on the left or right of the person playing chess##3
 4. the person playing domino is the person playing domino##1
 5. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
 6. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere between the owner of the fish and the owner of the cat##7
 7. the person playing scrabble is in an odd position##4
 8. the owner of the cat is in an even position##4
 9. the person playing whist is the owner of the goat##1
10. the person playing domino is between the person playing chess and the owner of the goldfish##2
11. the person playing monopoly is on the left or right of the owner of the cat##3
12. the owner of the goldfish is in the middle##1
13. the person playing chess is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
14. the person playing backgammon is on the left or right of the person playing domino##3
15. the person playing whist is on the far left##1
16. the person playing whist is somewhere to the left of the owner of the pony##5
17. the person playing monopoly is somewhere to the right of the owner of the cat##5
