 9. the person who's sport is skiing is somewhere to the right of the fan of folk##5
10. the fan of funk is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
11. the person who's sport is handball is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##5
12. the person who's sport is handball is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3
13. the fan of rock is somewhere between the person who's sport is skiing and the fan of metal##7
14. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the fan of indie##1
15. the fan of funk is the person who's sport is cricket##1
16. the fan of funk is on the left or right of the fan of salsa##3
17. the person who's sport is snowboarding is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is tennis##5
18. the fan of rock is on the right of the fan of reggae##1

